  "text": "To our knowledge, the current study is the first meta-analysis to provide comprehensive evidence for the effectiveness of psychosocial interventions on the quality of life of CRC patients. A total of eight randomized controlled trials (2117 patients overall) evaluating the application of psychosocial interventions for CRC patients were systematically reviewed, but only one of these studies, that of Hawkes et al. [CITATION_1] , identified a significant improvement in the quality of life of its intervention group.",
